see why Daphne was upset.

10:27.565 --> 10:31.401
We're aware that you were the
leader, that's why you're here.

10:31.436 --> 10:34.505
But as reckless as your actions were,

10:34.539 --> 10:37.441
your protest has forced the school board

10:37.475 --> 10:40.511
